She's a monster.

23
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:49,780
Currently, all the evidence points to Yu Bo.

24
00:03:49,780 --> 00:03:50,930
I've released Shen Anren

25
00:03:50,930 --> 00:03:51,930
and arrested Yu Bo

26
00:03:51,950 --> 00:03:53,810
according to your instructions.

27
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,390
It's really so frustrating that we've let Shen Anren

28
