31
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:05,980
I'll get evidence against him sooner or later.

32
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,320
Since he likes to play games,

33
00:04:09,820 --> 00:04:11,620
then I'll play the game with him.

34
00:04:16,709 --> 00:04:18,019
Is there anything else?

35
00:04:18,019 --> 00:04:20,269
When we were interrogating Yu Bo, we discovered that

36
00:04:20,269 --> 00:04:23,070
he was the one who had drugged Uncle Shen back then,

37
00:04:23,220 --> 00:04:24,420
which led to a relapse

38
00:04:24,460 --> 00:04:25,620
of his old disease.

39
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:27,340
After he got injured,

40
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:28,710
he died of his injuries.

41
00:04:28,710 --> 00:04:29,350
So,

42
00:04:29,740 --> 00:04:32,740
Qin Siyuan was not the murderer who killed Uncle Shen.

43
00:04:39,060 --> 00:04:39,990
I'm sorry.

44
00:04:40,580 --> 00:04:42,130
I didn't do that intentionally.

45
00:04:42,130 --> 00:04:43,530
I didn't know it would...

46
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,320
You're sorry?

47
00:04:49,590 --> 00:04:50,390
You're sorry?

48
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:52,960
You think saying sorry is enough?

49
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:54,230
Why was it you?

50
00:04:54,659 --> 00:04:56,050
Why must it be you?

51
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:07,670
It turns out that I've been wrongly blaming her all this time.

52
00:05:07,670 --> 00:05:08,360
Governor,

53
00:05:08,590 --> 00:05:11,190
