54
00:05:13,910 --> 00:05:15,070
She is my life.

55
00:05:28,590 --> 00:05:29,400
Anren!

56
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:33,190
Anren!

57
00:05:40,210 --> 00:05:40,900
Anren!

58
00:05:53,100 --> 00:05:54,180
Miss Su said that

59
00:05:54,470 --> 00:05:56,870
she would find someone to beat her up badly.

60
00:05:57,270 --> 00:05:58,600
Don't let her come back.

61
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,730
Leave through the back door.

62
00:05:59,730 --> 00:06:01,120
Make sure that you won't be discovered.

63
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:01,910
Don't worry.

64
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,270
Where is Qin Siyuan?

65
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,240
What do you mean?

66
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,150
Have you let Qin Siyuan go missing?

67
00:06:11,150 --> 00:06:12,610
How did you look after her?

68
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,550
Governor.

69
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:16,870
One of our subordinates said that

70
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:18,800
he saw Miss Su outside the mansion.

71
00:06:35,890 --> 00:06:36,530
My Lady.

72
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:37,960
She's really a monster.

73
00:06:38,070 --> 00:06:41,400
She's been beaten for so long, but she still hasn't died yet.

74
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,560
Shen Zheng,

75
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:45,520
why are you here?

76
00:06:45,670 --> 00:06:47,090
Have you regretted that...

77
00:06:47,090 --> 00:06:48,220
Where is Qin Siyuan?

78
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:50,970
Why are you still looking for her?

79
00:06:50,970 --> 00:06:52,170
She's just a monster.

80
00:06:52,190 --> 00:06:53,710
You guys have been deceived by her.

81
00:06:53,710 --> 00:06:54,510
Where is she?

82
00:06:54,540 --> 00:06:57,000
You're actually pointing a gun at me for her?

83
00:06:59,630 --> 00:07:01,870
Is there anyone else who wants to come up?

84
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:04,150
This person is a monster and won't die.

85
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:07,150
If any of you don't believe it,

86
00:07:07,150 --> 00:07:08,260
just give it a try.

87
00:07:09,670 --> 00:07:10,870
Shall we give it a try?

88
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:12,390
Let's go.

89
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,450
Let's give it a try.

90
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:19,070
This woman is quite pitiful.

91
00:07:19,070 --> 00:07:19,870
That's right.

92
00:07:20,220 --> 00:07:22,680
People have beaten her up so badly like that.

93
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,640
Check this place.

94
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:50,310
It's my fault.

95
00:07:50,550 --> 00:07:52,210
I'll take you back right away.

96
00:07:53,250 --> 00:07:54,780
I'll take her to leave here.

97
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,000
I've told you that

98
00:08:08,350 --> 00:08:09,260
we shouldn't

99
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:11,430
meet again in the future

100
00:08:12,550 --> 00:08:14,150
to avoid causing annoyance.

101
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:17,670
You remember it now?

102
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,560
As a dying person,

103
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:26,060
I shouldn't leave him with any lingering thoughts, should I?

104
00:08:30,190 --> 00:08:30,870
Okay.

105
00:08:34,659 --> 00:08:35,860
You can't go with him.

106
00:08:52,590 --> 00:08:54,150
If you dare to stop me again,

107
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:56,500
I'll kill you.

108
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:18,560
The wound hasn't healed yet,

109
00:09:18,590 --> 00:09:20,480
and my abilities have disappeared, too.

110
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,630
But I'm not dead.

111
00:09:22,100 --> 00:09:23,500
Why is that?

112
00:09:24,540 --> 00:09:25,570
Where's my lamp?

113
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:36,770
Where is my lamp?

114
00:09:37,430 --> 00:09:38,570
