115
00:09:38,570 --> 00:09:39,610
in utter disgust.

116
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,570
Can't we be the same as before?

117
00:09:41,670 --> 00:09:42,310
Just

118
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:43,110
dream

119
00:09:43,110 --> 00:09:43,750
on!

120
00:09:45,710 --> 00:09:46,750
Since you hate me,

121
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,830
why did you want to leave with me

122
00:09:47,830 --> 00:09:48,830
and give me hope?

123
00:09:49,350 --> 00:09:51,950
Are you trying to use me to push Shen Zheng away?

124
00:09:52,110 --> 00:09:52,870
Forget it.

125
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:54,730
None of this matters.

126
00:09:55,590 --> 00:09:57,640
As long as you can still stay by my side,

127
00:09:57,640 --> 00:09:58,810
I'll be content.

128
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:01,900
Get lost!

129
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,390
Am I really so unworthy of your affection?

130
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:07,120
How am I inferior to Shen Zheng?

131
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:09,430
You're not as good as him in every aspect.

132
00:10:09,430 --> 00:10:10,800
As for the grudge that you lied to me,

133
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,000
after I get the lamp,

134
00:10:12,250 --> 00:10:14,050
I'll get even with you properly.

135
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:20,110
She's a monster that can heal herself after getting injured.

136
00:10:20,110 --> 00:10:22,440
Why are you and Shen Zheng both on her side?

137
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,470
You're the real monster.

138
00:10:25,470 --> 00:10:26,990
If you make up stories to slander her again,

139
00:10:26,990 --> 00:10:27,960
I'll kill you!

140
00:10:28,310 --> 00:10:29,260
Let go of me!

141
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:31,700
If you don't want to lose her,

142
00:10:31,700 --> 00:10:33,140
I have a way to help you.
